---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Threads — Smooth Threads | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.", "canonical": "/services/smooth-threads", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-neutral-100 text-neutral-900">
  <!-- Split HERO (light) -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <nav class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-4">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <a href="/services" class="hover:text-neutral-700">Services</a>
      <span class="mx-1">/</span>
      <span class="text-neutral-800">Threads — Smooth Threads</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="md:col-span-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Threads — Smooth Threads</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600">Subtle collagen‑stimulating threads to refine and firm skin.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Consultation‑first</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Personalized plan</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-700">Clear aftercare</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-6 h-56 md:h-64 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-200 to-white shadow-sm"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sticky subnav -->
  <div class="sticky top-16 z-40 border-y border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-100/95 backdrop-blur">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="flex gap-3 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar py-3 text-sm">
        <a href="#overview" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Overview</a>
        <a href="#fit" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Who it’s for</a>
        <a href="#timeline" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Before • During • After</a>
        <a href="#indications" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Indications & Areas</a>
        <a href="#results" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Results & Longevity</a>
        <a href="#aftercare" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Aftercare</a>
        <a href="#compare" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">Compare</a>
        <a href="#faqs" class="shrink-0 rounded-full border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-1 text-neutral-700 hover:bg-neutral-50">FAQs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10">
      <section id="overview" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">This service is tailored to deliver refined, natural‑looking results while prioritizing comfort, safety, and education. We plan around your features and goals, explain each step, and set realistic expectations.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="fit" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Who it’s for / Who should avoid</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">A good fit</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Healthy individuals with realistic expectations</li>
              <li>Concerns aligned with the service capabilities</li>
              <li>Open to following aftercare</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium">Consider alternatives</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Certain medical conditions or medications</li>
              <li>Active infections/irritation in the area</li>
              <li>Unrealistic timelines or expectations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-500 text-sm">Educational only—not medical advice. Review your history with your provider.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="timeline" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Before • During • After</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">Before</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Consult & prep</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Goals, medical history, tailored plan, pre‑care tips.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">During</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Treatment</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Technique matched to indication and area; comfort‑forward approach.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500">After</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Aftercare</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm mt-1">Clear guidance, do’s & don’ts, and next‑steps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="indications" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Indications & Areas</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Mapped to your anatomy and goals</li>
          <li>Balanced, proportionate outcomes</li>
          <li>Discussed during consultation</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="results" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Results & Longevity</h3>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Onset</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Varies by service</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Peak</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Discussed at consult</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-300 bg-neutral-50 p-4"><p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm">Duration</p><p class="text-neutral-900 font-medium mt-1">Maintenance as advised</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="aftercare" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Aftercare Checklist</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-neutral-700 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Follow your personalized post‑care handout</li>
          <li>Protect the area and avoid irritants as directed</li>
          <li>Hydration, rest, and recommended products only</li>
          <li>Report unexpected reactions promptly</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="compare" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Compare Alternatives</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="min-w-full text-sm border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <thead class="bg-neutral-50">
              <tr>
                <th class="text-left font-medium text-neutral-700 p-3 border-b border-neutral-200">Option</th>
                <th class="text-left font-medium text-neutral-700 p-3 border-b border-neutral-200">Best for</th>
                <th class="text-left font-medium text-neutral-700 p-3 border-b border-neutral-200">Duration</th>
                <th class="text-left font-medium text-neutral-700 p-3 border-b border-neutral-200">Notes</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-neutral-200">
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-800">This service</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Your mapped indication</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">As advised</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Comfort‑forward, tailored</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-neutral-200">
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-800">Alternative A</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Different concern/area</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Varies</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Discuss pros/cons at consult</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-800">Alternative B</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Another approach</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Varies</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-neutral-700">Match to goals & timeline</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faqs" class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-neutral-700">
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">It varies by concern and modality. Your provider will outline a personalized plan and maintenance if appropriate.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Our approach focuses on subtle, harmonious changes that complement your features.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Most services have minimal downtime. Temporary redness, swelling, or sensitivity can occur and usually resolves quickly.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Side insights -->
    <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900">Key Facts</h4>
        <dl class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-neutral-700">
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Session length</dt><dd>~30–60 minutes</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Downtime</dt><dd>Minimal</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Discomfort</dt><dd>Mild to moderate</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-neutral-500">Maintenance</dt><dd>Personalized</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-300 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold text-neutral-900">Good to know</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-neutral-700">We’ll review your goals, medical history, and preferences to create a plan that fits your lifestyle and budget.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
